{
  "texts": [
    "Game developers and graphics creation communities have adopted GPT with integrated multiplatform capabilities, such as AutoGPT models.",
    "Many GPT-based cloud services are available for vertical business.",
    "Generative AI is seen as a solution to resource, automate, and increase quality in software development.",
    "GPTs may free high-level skills for more important tasks, reduce costs, and optimize resources.",
    "Many corporations have welcomed this, allowing them to shift engineers to new business models and to improve productivity (Ebert and Louridas 2023)."
  ]
}